701778f-a.title: Bronx: Sedgwick Avenue - Kingsbridge Road
701778f-a.text:
Sedgwick Avenue, at 4. Kingsbridge TToad, showing the public
place which was improved with benches by the W.P.A. The buildings
on the right are on the N.E. corner of the two thoroughfares; the
one on the left is on the N.W. corner.
January 27, 1937
